---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'top-picks', text: 'Top Picks', level: 2 },
  { id: 'what-global-nomads-need', text: 'What Global Nomads Need', level: 2 },
  { id: 'comparison-table', text: 'Plan Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'detailed-reviews', text: 'Detailed Reviews', level: 2 },
  { id: 'key-features', text: 'Key Features', level: 2 },
  { id: 'lifestyle-considerations', text: 'Lifestyle Considerations', level: 2 },
  { id: 'faqs', text: 'FAQs', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Digital Nomad Insurance', href: '/best/digital-nomad-insurance' },
  { title: 'Worldwide Insurance', href: '/best/worldwide-insurance' },
  { title: 'Multi-Country Insurance', href: '/best/multi-country-insurance' },
  { title: 'Cigna Global Review', href: '/providers/cigna-global' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing Review', href: '/providers/safetywing' },
];

const comparisonColumns = [
  { key: 'provider', header: 'Provider' },
  { key: 'globalCoverage', header: 'Global Coverage' },
  { key: 'flexibility', header: 'Flexibility' },
  { key: 'noBase', header: 'No Fixed Base OK' },
  { key: 'priceRange', header: 'Price Range' },
];

const comparisonRows = [
  { provider: 'Cigna Global', globalCoverage: 'Excellent', flexibility: 'Very High', noBase: 'Yes', priceRange: '$200-500/mo' },
  { provider: 'SafetyWing', globalCoverage: 'Good', flexibility: 'Very High', noBase: 'Yes', priceRange: '$45-100/mo' },
  { provider: 'Bupa Global', globalCoverage: 'Excellent', flexibility: 'High', noBase: 'Yes', priceRange: '$300-600/mo' },
  { provider: 'World Nomads', globalCoverage: 'Good', flexibility: 'High', noBase: 'Yes', priceRange: '$50-150/mo' },
  { provider: 'IMG Global', globalCoverage: 'Good', flexibility: 'Good', noBase: 'Yes', priceRange: '$100-300/mo' },
];

const featuresColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'importance', header: 'Why It Matters' },
  { key: 'whatToLookFor', header: 'What to Look For' },
];

const featuresRows = [
  { feature: 'No fixed base requirement', importance: 'Nomads move constantly', whatToLookFor: 'Policy works without fixed address' },
  { feature: 'Worldwide coverage', importance: 'Travel to many countries', whatToLookFor: 'True global coverage' },
  { feature: 'Easy address changes', importance: 'Locations change frequently', whatToLookFor: 'Simple admin process' },
  { feature: 'Telemedicine', importance: 'Healthcare access anywhere', whatToLookFor: '24/7 global telemedicine' },
  { feature: 'Evacuation coverage', importance: 'May be in remote areas', whatToLookFor: 'Good evacuation limits' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="Best Insurance for Global Nomads 2026"
  description="Compare international health insurance for global nomads living in multiple countries. Find plans with worldwide coverage, no fixed base requirements, and maximum flexibility."
  headline="Best Insurance for Global Nomads"
  subheadline="Living across multiple countries without a fixed home base? Global nomad insurance provides worldwide coverage with the flexibility your lifestyle demands."
  heroImage="/images/answers/best-global-nomad-insurance.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  showHeroCta={false}
  ctaButtonText="Compare Plans"
  ctaButtonHref="/compare/"
>
  <h2 id="top-picks">Top Picks for Global Nomads</h2>
  <p>
    These insurers offer the best options for location-independent living:
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🌍</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Comprehensive</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-2">Cigna Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Full health insurance with worldwide coverage, no fixed base required, and comprehensive benefits.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">💰</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Budget Option</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">SafetyWing</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Affordable coverage designed for nomads with subscription model and global access.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">👑</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Best Premium</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">Bupa Global</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Premium worldwide coverage for nomads wanting top-tier protection everywhere.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-3">🔑</div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Key Need</h3>
      <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-neutral-700 mb-2">True Flexibility</p>
      <p class="text-neutral-600">Coverage that works regardless of where you are or how often you move.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="what-global-nomads-need">What Global Nomads Need</h2>
  <p>
    Global nomads have unique insurance requirements:
  </p>

  <h3>No Fixed Base</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Moving between countries regularly</li>
    <li>No permanent home address</li>
    <li>May use mail forwarding services</li>
    <li>Insurance must accommodate this</li>
    <li>Traditional "country of residence" doesn't apply</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Worldwide Coverage</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Coverage in any country visited</li>
    <li>No advance notification of travel</li>
    <li>Same benefits everywhere</li>
    <li>Can receive care in any location</li>
    <li>True global network access</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Maximum Flexibility</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Easy to update location</li>
    <li>No penalties for moving</li>
    <li>Coverage adapts to lifestyle</li>
    <li>Simple administration</li>
    <li>Works with nomad lifestyle</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Coverage Without Borders"
    description="Compare insurance for location-independent lifestyles."
    buttonText="Compare Plans"
    buttonHref="/compare/"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="comparison-table">Global Nomad Plan Comparison</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={comparisonColumns} rows={comparisonRows} />
  </div>

  <h2 id="detailed-reviews">Detailed Reviews</h2>

  <h3>Cigna Global — Best Comprehensive</h3>
  <p>
    Cigna Global offers full international health insurance for global nomads.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>True worldwide coverage</li>
    <li>No fixed base required</li>
    <li>Comprehensive health benefits</li>
    <li>1.5M+ provider network</li>
    <li>Easy location updates</li>
    <li>24/7 telemedicine</li>
    <li>Guaranteed lifetime renewal</li>
    <li>Modular flexibility</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Higher price than travel-style options. Best for those wanting full health insurance. Worth it for comprehensive protection.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/cigna-global">Read our full Cigna Global review</a></p>

  <h3>SafetyWing — Best Budget Option</h3>
  <p>
    SafetyWing is designed specifically for nomads on a budget.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Subscription model ($45/mo starting)</li>
    <li>No fixed base required</li>
    <li>Cancel anytime flexibility</li>
    <li>Global coverage</li>
    <li>Designed for nomads</li>
    <li>Simple sign-up</li>
    <li>Good emergency coverage</li>
    <li>Telemedicine included</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Travel insurance style—not full health insurance. Lower limits ($250K). Best for young, healthy nomads. Good for emergency/catastrophic.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/safetywing">Read our full SafetyWing review</a></p>

  <h3>Bupa Global — Best Premium</h3>
  <p>
    Bupa Global provides premium coverage for global nomads.
  </p>
  <p><strong>What works well:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Excellent worldwide coverage</li>
    <li>No fixed base required</li>
    <li>Premium service quality</li>
    <li>Comprehensive benefits</li>
    <li>Strong global network</li>
    <li>24/7 support</li>
    <li>Lifetime renewal</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Considerations:</strong> Most expensive option. Best for nomads wanting top-tier coverage. Worth it for comprehensive protection.</p>
  <p><a href="/providers/bupa-global">Read our full Bupa Global review</a></p>

  <h2 id="key-features">Key Features for Global Nomads</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={featuresColumns} rows={featuresRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>No Fixed Base Requirements</h3>
  <p>
    Essential for nomads:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Policy doesn't require permanent address</li>
    <li>Can use mail forwarding service</li>
    <li>Coverage based on global, not country</li>
    <li>No penalties for frequent moves</li>
    <li>Simple location notification</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Telemedicine Access</h3>
  <p>
    Critical when constantly moving:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>See a doctor from anywhere</li>
    <li>24/7 availability across time zones</li>
    <li>Get prescriptions remotely</li>
    <li>Continuity of care while traveling</li>
    <li>Works with any internet connection</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Evacuation Coverage</h3>
  <p>
    Important for remote locations:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>May be in areas with limited healthcare</li>
    <li>Transport to adequate facilities</li>
    <li>Repatriation options</li>
    <li>24/7 coordination support</li>
    <li>High limits recommended</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Easy Administration</h3>
  <p>
    Nomad-friendly features:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Mobile app access</li>
    <li>Online claims submission</li>
    <li>Digital ID cards</li>
    <li>Simple location updates</li>
    <li>Email/digital communication</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Insurance for Your Lifestyle"
    description="Find coverage that moves with you."
    buttonText="Compare Plans"
    buttonHref="/compare/"
  />

  <h2 id="lifestyle-considerations">Lifestyle Considerations</h2>

  <h3>Slow Travel Nomads</h3>
  <p>
    Spending months in each location:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>May establish temporary residency</li>
    <li>Can benefit from local healthcare</li>
    <li>Annual plans work well</li>
    <li>More comprehensive coverage appropriate</li>
    <li>Consider long-term plan features</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Fast Travel Nomads</h3>
  <p>
    Moving frequently:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Multiple countries per month</li>
    <li>Need instant coverage everywhere</li>
    <li>Telemedicine especially valuable</li>
    <li>Flexible plans essential</li>
    <li>SafetyWing-style may suffice</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Visa Considerations</h3>
  <p>
    Insurance for visa requirements:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Many visas require health insurance</li>
    <li>Coverage letter may be needed</li>
    <li>Minimum coverage requirements vary</li>
    <li>Annual plans often required</li>
    <li>Verify specific visa needs</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Tax Residency</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Insurance doesn't establish tax residency</li>
    <li>Complex topic for nomads</li>
    <li>Consult tax professional</li>
    <li>Keep good records</li>
    <li>Separate issue from insurance</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Long-Term Considerations</h3>
  <p>
    Thinking ahead:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Guaranteed renewal protects future</li>
    <li>Conditions developed are covered</li>
    <li>May eventually settle somewhere</li>
    <li>Coverage can adapt to life changes</li>
    <li>Better to have than need later</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="faqs">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <h3>Can I get insurance without a permanent address?</h3>
  <p>
    Yes. Many international insurers accommodate global nomads without fixed addresses. You may need a contact address (mail forwarding works) but not a permanent residence. Cigna Global, SafetyWing, and others specifically serve this market.
  </p>

  <h3>What's the difference between digital nomad and global nomad insurance?</h3>
  <p>
    Largely the same market. "Digital nomad" often implies remote work while traveling. "Global nomad" is broader—anyone living location-independently. Insurance needs are similar: worldwide coverage, flexibility, no fixed base.
  </p>

  <h3>Do I need to notify my insurer when I move countries?</h3>
  <p>
    With worldwide plans, usually no for short visits. For longer stays or changing your "base" location, notification may be helpful but typically doesn't affect coverage. Check your specific policy terms.
  </p>

  <h3>Is travel insurance enough for global nomads?</h3>
  <p>
    Depends on your needs and risk tolerance. Travel insurance (like SafetyWing) is affordable and covers emergencies. For comprehensive health coverage including routine care and chronic conditions, full international health insurance is better.
  </p>

  <h3>What about pre-existing conditions?</h3>
  <p>
    Travel-style plans typically exclude them. Full international health plans offer options: moratorium (covered after stability period) or full underwriting. For chronic conditions, choose comprehensive over travel insurance.
  </p>

  <h3>Can global nomad insurance meet visa requirements?</h3>
  <p>
    Often yes. Annual international health plans usually meet visa insurance requirements. Travel insurance may or may not qualify. Check specific visa requirements and get coverage letters from your insurer if needed.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This content is for informational purposes only. Global nomad insurance options vary. We are not insurance brokers. Always verify current coverage directly with insurers.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
